data.description: Back on Market! Buyer financing fell thru - Don't Miss this INCREDIBLE Value! Gorgeous & Spacious 5 Bedroom-5 Bathroom, 3 Car Garage home located in exclusive Castle Ridge w-Nebbie Williams Elem. Downstairs features a luxurious primary suite w-huge walk-in closet, dedicated study and dining room while the open living concept provide ample space for family & entertainment. Showstopper kitchen has oversized island, granite countertops, elegantly painted cabinets, ceramic flooring, gas cooktop & stainless steel appliances. Upstairs offers a cozy getaway complete w-gameroom, media room, 4 large bedrooms-each having their own bathroom access. The dining room offers flex-space options as a barn door was installed for privacy making a 6th bedroom-with full bath, craft room, or exercise space easy to accomplish. Great backyard has covered patio, pre-wired for surround sound & newly stained fence. Perfect location--Super Clean & Ready for immediate Move-in.
